{
  "stem": "6777.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once they closed the ghetto there had been gates which had been guarded by German SS people, men, and you couldn't get in or out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was some time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in the initial period, it was possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, as a matter of fact, some of my friends had been working for them, for the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until it was closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That depends.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There had been different reactions from different people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There had been-- there had been the people who had been friendly and tried to help, and that was the minority.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The majority was very happy that the Jews were taken out of the larger city and closed away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the typhus was rife amongst the Jewish population because of the terrific crowding, and those people who survived they still had been carriers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Therefore, they couldn't go back into their homes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to come to the quarantine hospital and stay there and recuperate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At least they got some food and proper care for a couple of weeks at least.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they'd be discharged and could go back to their homes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this quarantine was in a former Polish gymnasium school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a beautiful library.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] street.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very close to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "40, 50, around this much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes more, sometimes less.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish Council had-- called Hospital and Medical Department.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fliederbaum who was well known to the community.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because before the war Warsaw had a very good Jewish hospital in a part which was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was very eminent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was-- there had been other doctors, as well, who came now and again to see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Judenrat, the council-- Jewish Council.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they had a budget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Economic Department had budgeting for every other department.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
